HEADWORD: Odd Fellow
<hw>Odd" Fel`low</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A member of a secret order, or
fraternity, styled the <membof>Independent Order of Odd
Fellows</membof>, established for mutual aid and social
enjoyment.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

